  "texts": [
    "We refer to the recent survey (Tang et al., 2023) for a more detailed introduction.",
    "2) Specialized Video-LLMs exploit frozen LLMs or general-purpose image MLLMs (e.g., BLIP-2 (Li et al., 2023a), LLaVA (Liu et al., 2023), LLaMA-Adapter (Zhang et al., 2024b)) while finetuning adaptor or LoRA (Hu et al., 2021) modules on target VideoQA datasets.",
    "Successful examples include Frozen-BiLM (Yang et al., 2022), SeViLA (Yu et al., 2023), LLaMA-VQA (Ko et al., 2023).",
    "Additionally, Video-LLaMA (Zhang et al., 2023b) is a general-purpose Video-LLM, but in this paper we study its finetuned version (Xiao et al., 2024) that is similar to LLaMA-Adapter but with Video Q-Former to encapsulate short clips of a video.",
    "3) Tool-based Video-LLMs."
  ],
